# Package changelogs

## [0.1.5]

- Added an init() method to curl client to initialize the client after release is called

## [0.2.0]

- Bug fix release in send and prepareOptions
- Breaking changes for prepareOptions parameter

## [0.3.0] Minor breaking changes

- Removed deprecated psr18 client implementation
- To minize requirements of the library and reduce package dependencies size, we remove psr18 dependencies


## [0.4.0] 2024-05-23

- Upgraded supported php version to >=7.2
- Set phpunit dev dependency to >=8.0
- Added `Response`, `JsonResponse` classes and `DecodeResponseHeaders` trait to the util namespace for parsing curl response